SIMPLE: mouthful
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mouthful
<hw>Mouth"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Mouthfuls</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>As much as
is usually put into the mouth at one time.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence, a small quantity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A statement that has a profound truth in it; <as>as,
you said a <ex>mouthful</ex>!</as></def> <mark>[informal]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mouthless</ent>⟦br⟧
